name: ✴ 𝕾𝖕𝖆𝖈𝖊 𝕾𝖍𝖊𝖑𝖑 ✴
description:
✴ Portrait of Space Shell

A head explodes at the beginning of time. Some star still hasn't gotten out of the shell. Some still orbit around it. Some stars fall off the gravity, but some remains. Like human thoughts.


✴[MAD GOD]✴ is an original dark fantasy series consist of blood and beautiful creatures portraying their life, their pride, and their attitude.
